Delicious tapas!  Here is our breakdown:1) patatas braves - nice fresh cut fries, delicious sauces (red one a little spicy)2) meat potato croquette / bombetta - delicious and rich3) grilled leeks with olive tapenade - yum, quite large might wanna ask for 1/2 portion if you are just 2 people4) beef cheek - very tender, could have used a little more salt Going again tonight cause I want to try their Fideua (was too full after going to Xampanyet right across the street beforehand) - everything other people were ordering looked delicious as well!
